## Additional Notes

### About the Developer
This Weather Assistant App was developed by hafizullahkhokhar1 as an open-source project to provide a beautiful, functional weather application for desktop users worldwide, with special attention to Pakistani weather patterns and travel safety.

### Third-Party Services
This software uses the following third-party services:
- OpenWeatherMap API for weather data
- IPInfo.io for location detection

Users are responsible for obtaining their own API keys for production use and complying with the terms of service of these providers.

### Contributions
Contributions, issues, and feature requests are welcome! Feel free to check the issues page and contribute to the project.

### Contact
- GitHub: https://github.com/hafizullahkhokhar1
- Email: hafizullahkhokhar1@gmail.com

### Disclaimer
This software is provided for informational purposes only. Weather data is provided by third-party services and the accuracy cannot be guaranteed. Users should not rely solely on this application for critical weather-related decisions.

For official weather warnings and alerts, please consult your local meteorological service.
